Reclusa::

She awoke feeling her whole form tingle.  She flexed her hands and
arms and felt the knew skin that covered them.  She very slowly sat up
and looked at herself.  She loked around until her optics rested on
Perceptor. "You are a genius."  She turned and slowly lowered herself
off the table. "Hmmm, now I really do feel comfortable in my skin." 
She glanced down and noticed a few other changes. "Hmm, new blaster
ports I see. You have really outdone yourself. I shall sing your
praise to your superior. Infact, I would recommend he under go an up
grade like this himself. You truely have done well." 
She was in fact very impressed with his skill. She knew that to have
this bot on her side later would be her greatest advantage.
